{
  "title": "Hemorragia Intracerebral",
  "guid": "4AEA4C832119A553730BC08E",
  "filepath": "/sessions/bold-jolly-cerf/mnt/Dropbox/- Esquemas/- Entidades clínicas/Neurología/Wiki. Hemorragia Intracerebral-2025.smmx",
  "root": {
    "id": "0",
    "parent": "-1",
    "text": "Hemorragia\nIntracerebral",
    "guid": "cp549nQLcl49zpapL75Cdw",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "1",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Definición y\nEpidemiología",
        "guid": "fj8hKEeD5r8Ec94aFMwP2Q",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "2",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "Emergencia neurológica",
            "guid": "SMQOLl9uRXkz4KUcLU5E4g",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "3",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "20-30% de los ACV",
            "guid": "KwTCizC0f70wjtL0VABU2Q",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "4",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "2da causa de ACV después del isquémico",
            "guid": "fc3ZkGB2UC5wtjvsPtgzTA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "5",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "Hemorragia en parénquima cerebral por rotura no traumática de vasos encefálicos penetrantes",
            "guid": "e3ZdnWnanL42gxa5ZbaQHw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "6",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "Pronóstico relacionado\ncon tamaño y localización",
            "guid": "G5km6gdX4BpglrnIEgxMiA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "7",
                "parent": "6",
                "text": ">60cc: Mortalidad 93% (profundas), 72% (lobulares)",
                "guid": "UkIsnQGwXxwFGA0WROCllA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "8",
                "parent": "6",
                "text": "<30cc: Mortalidad 39% (profundas), 7% (lobulares)",
                "guid": "dbvRekLmo8B0nugLc_ryog",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "9",
            "parent": "1",
            "text": "Incidencia: 12-15 casos/100. 000 habitantes/año, ↑ con la edad y estilos de vida no saludables",
            "guid": "CmqKf3kSxiUIxwJ7Uy6YrQ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "10",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Localización:",
        "guid": "WIELnzynp5cAfN2PA4XOKg",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "11",
            "parent": "10",
            "text": "35-70% en áreas profundas (ganglios basales, tálamo) → HTA (HIC típica)",
            "guid": "bVwnVDELsINXhiMEayoA5Q",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "12",
            "parent": "10",
            "text": "15-30% en lóbulos → 40% HTA y CAA",
            "guid": "EYIAskg8XvAqAjQxDPheTw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "13",
            "parent": "10",
            "text": "5-10% en fosa posterior (cerebelo, tronco)",
            "guid": "Mhb7r2CFSutyru5uTbAimQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "14",
            "parent": "10",
            "text": "Sitios más comunes: Putamen, tálamo, cerebelo, puente",
            "guid": "Z90rBVNFqDdfvG8hOh9Xog",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "15",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Fisiopatología",
        "guid": "VPYHU2TUfDh-__02SrHYzQ",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "16",
            "parent": "15",
            "text": "Ruptura de arterias parenquimatosas cerebrales",
            "guid": "J7sf-HOe5UE-rMtwMiWqdw",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "17",
            "parent": "15",
            "text": "Teoría de Charcot-Bouchard: Aneurismas en arterias perforantes por HTA crónica",
            "guid": "bLGrZ0dzzesFVEMlRTK3Bg",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "18",
            "parent": "15",
            "text": "Clasificación:",
            "guid": "BBt1gwXRILRIuIUwcXec1w",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "19",
                "parent": "18",
                "text": "Primaria (85%):\nHTA, CAA",
                "guid": "NtzROCA-qDRcoZ28SF7R6g",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "20",
                    "parent": "19",
                    "text": "HTA: FR independiente de sexo y edad, presente en 60% de los casos,\ncausa alteraciones degenerativas en vasos cerebrales",
                    "guid": "aHsHJQaj0e5VVzA5GpIC1A",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "21",
                    "parent": "19",
                    "text": "CAA: 1ra causa de HIC lobar en adulto mayor, hemorragias múltiples,\n↑ recurrencia, demencia vascular, alelos ApoE son FR genético",
                    "guid": "Zykc2UgGHqhoQiVtTwZH3g",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "22",
                "parent": "18",
                "text": "Secundaria:",
                "guid": "G0vG30f-lI8JJZ-AcEHOMg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "23",
                    "parent": "22",
                    "text": "Malformaciones vasculares congénitas o adquiridas (1/3 de HIC en jóvenes)",
                    "guid": "LNMQxwglnLc686b_VI4wvw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "24",
                    "parent": "22",
                    "text": "Tumores (primarios o metastásicos)",
                    "guid": "e8SB-Hmgcm8Gs9s2aHYtXw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "25",
                    "parent": "22",
                    "text": "Transformación hemorrágica de ACV isquémico",
                    "guid": "QRRAWwwIHlstqORlRS-13g",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "26",
                    "parent": "22",
                    "text": "Anticoagulantes, fibrinolíticos, antiagregantes (rTPA → HIC lobares y multifocales)",
                    "guid": "Edk_EHZhaZY2p1K1SLYQSA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "27",
                    "parent": "22",
                    "text": "Drogas simpático-miméticas (cocaína, anfetaminas, descongestionantes nasales)",
                    "guid": "FqARyhNI8HIRFOIyfxsY7w",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "28",
                    "parent": "22",
                    "text": "Coagulopatías (déficit de Factor Von Willebrand, hemofilia, trombocitopenia, vasculitis)",
                    "guid": "GezCYGZsEmsZrRvDARXfOQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "29",
            "parent": "15",
            "text": "Mecanismo de\ndaño:",
            "guid": "LnIxEwHvQTFQHCcXSb338g",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "30",
                "parent": "29",
                "text": "Disrupción mecánica por sangre",
                "guid": "Se3VwFlBxpc5_8YkdsDmhw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "31",
                "parent": "29",
                "text": "Disección del tejido parenquimatoso",
                "guid": "YWdjTnTzbSRLTxdGXSvlRw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "32",
                "parent": "29",
                "text": "Edema e inflamación perihemorrágica (edema vasogénico por ruptura de BHE)",
                "guid": "bpPfk1IC8nxFohKmL6gf7g",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "33",
            "parent": "15",
            "text": "Expansión del hematoma: Hasta 6 h (sin coagulopatías), hasta 24 h (con coagulopatías)",
            "guid": "XgsQ2HNK9wx019XMb-RP6A",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "34",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Manifestaciones\nClínicas",
        "guid": "aaxgoit_KII4mmAwAExybA",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "35",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Similar a ACV isquémico, clínicamente no se pueden diferenciar",
            "guid": "PsgY9EmvQmJ_Z4tcWLTbVA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "36",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Sugieren HIC: Cefalea, náuseas, vómitos, ↓ nivel de conciencia, crisis hipertensiva, hipertonía en sitio de paresia",
            "guid": "MBtUzRkUpx9ZyrqNXo2F4Q",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "37",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Se requiere neuroimágenes para diagnóstico y manejo",
            "guid": "GwPoUCnm4aQoS33TZPG-EA",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "38",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Síntomas y signos: Déficit neurológico focal de\ninstalación brusca, progresa con las horas",
            "guid": "AyioO2JLQ_hbsqSXZJALig",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "39",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "Motor: Paresias (mono, di, hemi, para)",
                "guid": "Vz6xHCcBu91Bu_DRRdKQrw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "40",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "Sensitivo: Termoalgésica, propioceptiva, especial",
                "guid": "eQSuWgdeA3d1erCeVw-_Mg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "41",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "Lenguaje: Afasia de expresión, comprensión, transcortical",
                "guid": "eqj6g2pShmpG9A8aZFVbJQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "42",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "Visual: Hemianopsias, cuadrantanopsias",
                "guid": "FdGu7H-Ob0pkoc2SVJnH4A",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "43",
                "parent": "38",
                "text": "Cerebeloso: Dismetría, disdiadococinesia, disinergia, hipotonía",
                "guid": "ST2xrGQJWO4tTqM0eVkGeQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "44",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Alteración de conciencia: ↑ PIC, hidrocefalia, compresión de tronco, herniación, epilepsia",
            "guid": "fR4ADQcZXcFX5oxaGCHoXg",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "45",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "↑ PA en 90% de los casos, posible crisis hipertensiva",
            "guid": "MQA_ZQAyCi59E6ZuNCjnoQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "46",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Antecedentes:",
            "guid": "Yn1OJljGSwYYuPMrObv_Qg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "47",
                "parent": "46",
                "text": "Fármacos (anticoagulantes, descongestivos\nnasales, píldoras adelgazantes, estimulantes)",
                "guid": "f8gG41p04_x_jo_xeMy1PQ",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "48",
                "parent": "46",
                "text": "Trauma o cirugía reciente (endarterectomía, angioplastia carotídea)",
                "guid": "YdLnc3UJQI9P3HRvXHvh9w",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "49",
                "parent": "46",
                "text": "Enfermedad sistémica asociada a coagulopatía (insuficiencia hepática, vasculitis, cáncer)",
                "guid": "X1vG-hbQg4lA0T0cdS115g",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "50",
                "parent": "46",
                "text": "Historia familiar de enfermedades neurológicas con riesgo de sangrado (MAV, aneurismas)",
                "guid": "Fl7y0yVzCq5Jxz3HX5ykfw",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "51",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Evaluación\nClínica",
            "guid": "CXxjnHcV4PtY9ar5Bppjqg",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "52",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "Anamnesis completa: Síntomas, signos, medicamentos, trauma, malignidad,\nMAV, cirugías cerebrales recientes, drogas, FR para coagulopatías",
                "guid": "fi8-vTDcN1MevEwILy9-Ig",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "53",
                    "parent": "52",
                    "text": "Hora de inicio de síntomas o\núltima vez visto bien",
                    "guid": "MQ5BgRvP8nZjWGXDE4uPpw",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "54",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "Examen físico: Signos vitales, examen neurológico,\nsignos de trauma en cabeza, cuello o cuerpo",
                "guid": "dJY9fHwRWO5NR47pdF5EYA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "55",
                    "parent": "54",
                    "text": "Glasgow ≤8 → intubación orotraqueal",
                    "guid": "VoY86kzWHtttKvmdOFkkXg",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "56",
                    "parent": "54",
                    "text": "FOUR: Mejor validez que Glasgow, útil en herniación y pacientes intubados",
                    "guid": "Qd9faj0Hbg0U1QZVITsmZA",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "57",
                "parent": "51",
                "text": "Escalas de evaluación y pronóstico:\nEscala de ICH (Hemphill 2001)",
                "guid": "U9fxllWmQ3EWaJxLajbkag",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "58",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Exámenes a\nsolicitar:",
            "guid": "exlOIGAv2hJJ04jpBJWxvA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "59",
                "parent": "58",
                "text": "TC de cerebro sin contraste:\nÁrea hiperdensa en parénquima",
                "guid": "V0W7DSLJM-ILMBVmVXT5yg",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "60",
                    "parent": "59",
                    "text": "Evolución: Hiperdensa → isodensa → hipodensa",
                    "guid": "U6VrNinsYW4EpHftBLOstw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "61",
                    "parent": "59",
                    "text": "Cálculo de volumen: ABC/2 (A: diámetro mayor, B: diámetro perpendicular a A, C: número de cortes x grosor, todo en cm)",
                    "guid": "RbxT5Wf83bAYPzxfOlKRYQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "62",
                    "parent": "59",
                    "text": "Expansión: ↑ absoluto >6 ml o >33% en siguiente TC",
                    "guid": "ZA42n2WGy0gusNXBOpRziQ",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "63",
                "parent": "58",
                "text": "AngioTC o TC con contraste: Si HIC asociada a aneurisma, MAV,\nlocalizaciones atípicas o pacientes jóvenes sin causa conocida",
                "guid": "MlzqIxvbz19y7ZfndDxJjg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "64",
                "parent": "58",
                "text": "RM con contraste: Estudio de lesión secundaria",
                "guid": "WOM9bAfCnjwVd2_yLLsvAg",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "65",
            "parent": "34",
            "text": "Descartar otras etiologías: Historia, examen físico, pruebas de coagulación",
            "guid": "XWjhrivgDD0W8hNsWIIvzg",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "66",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Manejo",
        "guid": "DA_mT2DFnFZdF-GKY1WhXQ",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "67",
            "parent": "66",
            "text": "Manejo inicial: Corrección de coagulopatía, tratamiento de HTA, evitar ↑ PIC",
            "guid": "A47QOGhH9vE4ypsnVzQ7bg",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "68",
            "parent": "66",
            "text": "Tratamiento\nMédico",
            "guid": "EjRYXz1vExRb5-gmV_CsRA",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "69",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "ABCDE, asegurar vía aérea y hemodinamia",
                "guid": "JWvwxXQnJIUSQz2mCXonZA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "70",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "SatO2 >94%, suplementar oxígeno si es necesario, intubación si falla respiratoria o Glasgow ≤8",
                "guid": "Wa3vzUD0E2dEDprtDArZ8Q",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "71",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "Ingreso a UTIN o UTAC",
                "guid": "XM_ixjb8MtUARyN_NbMgMg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "72",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "Normalizar glicemia (140-180 mg/dL) y temperatura (paracetamol si fiebre, buscar foco infeccioso y tratar)",
                "guid": "Pr7RERW-k3Fibk81HCeyvw",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "73",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "PAS <140-160 mmHg: ↓ riesgo de expansión\ndel hematoma, mejora pronóstico funcional",
                "guid": "QZ6fr3lgYqF0qeKNTa6F_g",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "74",
                    "parent": "73",
                    "text": "Antihipertensivos: Captopril, labetalol, urapidil (1ra línea),\nnitroglicerina (refractariedad o contraindicación)",
                    "guid": "WiX-91HBxBgxBCdbXbTPMA",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "id": "75",
                "parent": "68",
                "text": "Revertir anticoagulantes o\nantiagregantes:",
                "guid": "Ogm7CWnOwoM06QqeTD4TaA",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "id": "76",
                    "parent": "75",
                    "text": "Antagonistas de Vitamina K: Vitamina K, complejo protrombínico",
                    "guid": "Jz3VlxDQ8sQkLr-tTKnGXA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "77",
                    "parent": "75",
                    "text": "Dabigatrán: Idarucizumab",
                    "guid": "BPgXSTZx_VNWI-3AXqYHFw",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "78",
                    "parent": "75",
                    "text": "Inhibidores del Factor X: Concentrado protrombínico o plasma fresco",
                    "guid": "d2YQuhoyiK5qsOEIVDXzgQ",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "79",
                    "parent": "75",
                    "text": "Heparina: Sulfato de protamina (1 mg por c/100 U de heparina, máx 50 mg)",
                    "guid": "US67g2r4BIcJ6ROzD-2MlA",
                    "children": []
                  },
                  {
                    "id": "80",
                    "parent": "75",
                    "text": "Antiagregantes: Considerar desmopresina",
                    "guid": "ALaX-GxXYugsFT9UQlU3pw",
                    "children": []
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "81",
            "parent": "66",
            "text": "Manejo de PIC:",
            "guid": "ZbfFiiC_IeEQA72mP93EgQ",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "82",
                "parent": "81",
                "text": "Instalación de DVE si hidrocefalia",
                "guid": "coDl-UEH5QEdkpOxLIqhAg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "83",
                "parent": "81",
                "text": "Posición semisentada 30-45°",
                "guid": "KtanhFJ7nlB4yLRrUhR9HA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "84",
                "parent": "81",
                "text": "Manitol (0.25-1 g/kg EV) o salino hipertónico 3% (3-4 cc/kg) o 10% (1-2 cc/kg)",
                "guid": "Y0yRFBz3dBgevkN4aESoXg",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "85",
                "parent": "81",
                "text": "Hiperventilación en VMI (rescate, monitorizar con catéter bulbo yugular)",
                "guid": "U2lxa3TiMTlG6q91Ss-CJQ",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "86",
            "parent": "66",
            "text": "Manejo de convulsiones: No profilaxis, tratar si hay convulsiones al debut,\nelegir anticonvulsivante según características del paciente",
            "guid": "HJOVBCjuiVpwMQH-HUos_A",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "87",
        "parent": "0",
        "text": "Tratamiento\nQuirúrgico",
        "guid": "FUXsQhxGQVJfn2Skev2xzA",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "88",
            "parent": "87",
            "text": "Controversial, riesgo puede ser mayor, difícil abordaje en ganglios basales",
            "guid": "PQVjNG-jIko623ZOL4ZJLQ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "89",
            "parent": "87",
            "text": "Indicaciones:",
            "guid": "MKsHS1huCf9cEOowW4Gu0A",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "90",
                "parent": "89",
                "text": "Hematoma lobar a 1 cm de corteza, >30 ml, deterioro neurológico",
                "guid": "KumoT1TZnpstlivsDjY5ZA",
                "children": []
              },
              {
                "id": "91",
                "parent": "89",
                "text": "Hemorragia cerebelar >3 cm con compresión de tronco, hidrocefalia o deterioro neurológico (acompañar de DVE si hidrocefalia)",
                "guid": "cdESs0xUb2R2euHCRTqEHg",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
